        'providerDesc' => 'Currently only OpenAI is actively used (AI_PROVIDER=openai in .env). The codebase contains integration code for AnythingLLM (app/AI/Services/AnythingLLMClient.php) and OpenWebUI (app/AI/Services/OpenWebUIClient.php), but these were never deployed or used in production — they are not ready for use. If you see references to these providers, you can ignore them.',
        'architectureTitle' => 'Architecture',
        'architectureDesc' => 'AI integration follows the Manager pattern for provider switching:',
        'architectureItems' => [
            'manager' => 'AIManager (app/AI/AIManager.php) — Factory that creates the correct AI client based on the AI_PROVIDER config. Currently only creates OpenAIClient.',
            'openai' => 'OpenAIClient (app/AI/Services/OpenAIClient.php) — Direct integration with OpenAI API. Handles chat completions and assistant threads.',
            'email' => 'OpenAIServiceEmail (app/Services/OpenAIServiceEmail.php) — Specialized service for processing supplier emails. Sends email content to GPT-3.5-turbo with a structured prompt and parses the response to extract hotel/booking data.',
