        'configTitle' => 'Configuration',
        'configDesc' => 'Set these in .env: OPENAI_KEY (your API key from platform.openai.com), OPENAI_MODEL (default: gpt-4.1 for chat, gpt-3.5-turbo for email processing), AI_PROVIDER=openai. The API key is required — without it, email processing and chat features will not work.',
